PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Michael Rene GARRETT, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157544
COA: 341352 Supreme Court of Michigan. March 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's September 12, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that reconsideration of our previous order is warranted. MCR 7.311(G). The motions for miscellaneous relief are DENIED.
